## Hook 规范（复杂页）

```ts
// hooks/useTaskList.ts
import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue'
import { GetTaskList } from '../services'
import type { TaskItem } from '../types'

export const useTaskList = () => {
  const tasks = ref<TaskItem[]>([])
  const loading = ref(false)

  const reload = async () => {
    loading.value = true
    try {
      const res = await GetTaskList({})
      tasks.value = res.data || []
    } finally {
      loading.value = false
    }
  }

  onMounted(reload)
  return { tasks, loading, reload }
}
```

- 每个 hook **只负责一个数据域**
- 返回 `{ data, loading, reload }` 等稳定命名
- hook 内不操作 DOM、不访问 router（编排放 index.vue）

